            sh:in ( "BanktegoedBinnenland" "BanktegoedBuitenland" "Aandelen" "Obligaties" "Beleggingsfondsen" "Derivaten" "Cryptovaluta" "OnroerendeZaakOverig" "Vordering" "Schuld" ) ;
            sh:maxCount 1 ;
            sh:minCount 1 ;
            sh:order 3 ;
